{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_03",
  "title": "愛歌う星の継承者 3話 ラブストーリーは突然に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ、まずは一通り聴かせてくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ could you let me listen to it first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "『Precious』は歌えるよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you sing \"Precious\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、歌えますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I can sing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "尊敬する麻奈様の大好きな曲ですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a beloved song of Mana-sama‚ whom I admire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "歌えはするんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can sing it‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ん？　どうした？　なんだか元気がないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What's wrong? You seem a bit down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "顔色悪くないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you feeling unwell?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "な、なんでもありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ it's nothing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私は出来る子、私は出来る子……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm capable‚ I'm capable…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファイッ、すず！　さあ、元気をお出しなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Suzu! Come on‚ show your energy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "元気があればなんでも出来る！　らしいですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I have energy‚ I can do anything! Apparently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……何をぶつぶつ言ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you muttering about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これは自己暗示をかけて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is self-affirmation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、なんでもありませんわ。早く曲を流して下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's nothing. Please play the song quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、じゃあいくぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ then let's begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "――ごくり、すずファイッですわ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gulp It's Suzu-fight!…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Two hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……全然ダメです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… It's completely no good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、もう一度、お願いしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please once again‚ I beg you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、今日はもうやめておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ let's stop for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、まだです！　まだ私は歌えますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not over yet! I can still sing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしてやめるのか分からないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you understand why we're stopping?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日のすず、声が全然出ていないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your voice isn't coming out at all today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつもなら、自分で気付いているはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ you would notice it yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？　どこか具合が悪いのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……実は、昨日、麻奈様のライブ映像を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Actually‚ yesterday‚ I watched Mana-sama's video…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと観て研究をしたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I studied it for a long time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もしかして、昨日寝てないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that you didn't sleep yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ調子が悪いのは当たり前だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why you're not feeling well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん、私、分かりませんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san‚ I don't understand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうして、麻奈様の曲を私が歌うのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why am I the one singing Mana-sama's songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、私を選んだのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did you choose me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうか……。俺の説明不足で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It's because of my lack of explanation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すずを悩ませてしまったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've caused Suzu to worry. I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。ちゃんと説明するから、外に出よう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll explain properly‚ let's go outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（ああ、私の体調管理ミスで{user}さんに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ah‚ because of my poor health management‚ )",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2,
      "sfxList": []
